{"tid":1953364,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果向中國捐款加碼至逾5,000萬人幣以應對疫情","createTime":"2020-04-01T06:55:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T07:55:25.000Z","uid":61257,"like":4,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"232d975034b963c94a8642dbe90d255a2b994ba3","tid":1953364,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"蘋果公司行政總裁庫克在微博上表示，蘋果將向中國的捐款加碼一倍以上至超過5,000萬人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n庫克稱，蘋果已通過在北京的中國扶貧基金會捐贈2,000萬元人民幣，用於支持湖北6間醫院，當中包括武漢的雷神山醫院，而其餘的捐款會用於支持中國長期公共衛生工作。<br />\n<br />\n他有微博上指，在疫情爆發期間，中國表現出令人難以置信的應變能力，感謝蘋果的團隊、合作夥伴及客戶在這些艱難時期所給予的支持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4016cf57744c5ad38f8f5aaffa131852808597e9","tid":1953364,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"交黨費"},{"pid":"80425bbffdf098e51378cbc052f438956b84331b","tid":1953364,"uid":215341,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T06:56:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54027c